                    Service clientèle<br><br>
                    contact@cloud-quizz.fr
                </p>
                <img src="{{asset('images/background/spaceman-4160023_960_720.webp')}}" class="img-fluid mt-4 col-12 col-lg-4" alt="spaceman" id="spaceman">
            </div>
